OL,5, Artificial intelligence is set to      
OL,6, affect nearly 40% of all jobs,         
OL,7, according to a new analysis by the     
OL,8, International Monetary Fund (IMF).     
OL,10,FIMF's managing director Kristalina     
OL,11,FGeorgieva says "in most scenarios, AI  
OL,12,Fwill likely worsen overall inequality".
OL,14,FMs Georgieva adds that policymakers    
OL,15,Fshould address the "troubling trend" to
OL,16,F"prevent the technology from further   
OL,17,Fstoking social tensions".              
OL,19,FThe proliferation of AI has put its    
OL,20,Fbenefits and risks under the spotlight.
